    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a concours-level 2001 BMW M3, a quintessential example of the E46 chassis. At its heart lies the S54 3.2L atmospheric straight-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure VANOS system that has been fully overhauled for precision timing. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The chassis has undergone comprehensive subframe reinforcement, a critical preventative measure for this platform, and retains its factory-spec suspension kinematics. This vehicle exhibits zero mechanical lash and maintains an impeccable exterior finish. Truly a turn-key specimen for the discerning collector.",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
