      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, maintained to the highest standards of excellence. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero imperfections, while the interior still carries that fresh, factory aroma. Every stitch in the premium leather is perfect, and the dashboard remains untouched by the sun. Mechanically, it performs exactly as it did the day it rolled off the lot, supported by a comprehensive folder of service records. From the pristine alloy wheels to the spotless engine bay, this car is ready for a collector or a discerning driver who accepts nothing less than perfection. It has been strictly garage-kept and professionally detailed, ensuring it remains in showroom state.",
      "price": 46500.0,
